\par\pard\plain \tx240\tx720\li720\fi-720\ltrch\loch \ls7\ilvl0{\listtext\f3\fs24\b0\i1	\loch\af3\hich\af3\dbch\af3\uc1\u9679\'3F	}{\f3\fs24\b0\i1 \loch\af3\hich\af3\dbch\af3\uc1\u8220\'93What is more, improvements in psychology and neuroscience have lent even more credence to the reader-response position, as we are now able to offer scientific proof \endash  the 'facts' that the Formalists were so keen on \endash  as to what is happening in an audience's mind when they engage with a literary work.\u8221\'94 }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 (Literature & The Brain, 2009)}
